title: Spacious home with backyard built in grill walk to Milburn Park
posting_body: ['Video tour: https://youtu.be/5fY2rPY-z0Q', "Don't miss this opportunity to live in such a hot area!", 'Located within walking distance of Milburn Park, residents can enjoy soccer fields, tennis courts, baseball field, covered pavilion, a pool and year round festivities; walking distance to excellent schools; a blink from 1890 Ranch & Lakeline Mall shopping and minutes to Lake Travis.', 'Master suite has a sitting area/office, upstairs 2nd living/game room.', 'Oversized outdoor living space with stone patio, built in grill, bar, and pergola.', 'New Garage doors!', 'All stainless steel appliances included (washer/dryer/fridge/dishwasher/gas range/range hood).', 'All indoor/outdoor furniture is for display purpose only.', 'Home is unfurnished.', 'The soaring entry, high ceilings and bedroom layout make this a wonderful home!', 'questions, tour request or to apply:', '<URL>', 'online 3D tour:', '<URL>', 'For more information, call us at', 'show contact info', 'Save money at move-in with our security deposit program using Rhino!', 'A small monthly fee ($10-20) covers your security deposit requirement.', 'Ask about our Rhino deposit program during the application and avoid the upfront security deposit payment.', 'Professionally managed by Darwin Homes, located in 20+ Markets, with 24 hr. maintenance for an exceptional resident experience.']
